<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome Email</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #fff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .btn {
      background-color: #4CAF50;
      border: none;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      text-align: center;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 16px;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
    .btn:hover {
      background-color: #45a049;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <p>Hi <%= firstName %>! 👋</p>
    <p>Welcome to Baristretto, we're thrilled to have you with us! 🎉🙏</p>
    <p>We're all a big community here, so make sure to search for your favorite coffee or the one that you're enjoying these days. ☕</p>
    <p>If it doesn't exist, help us grow and create the bean! 🌱</p>
    <table role="presentation" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td align="left">
            <table role="presentation" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
              <tbody>
                <tr>
                  <td>
                    <a class="btn" href="<%= url %>" target="_blank">Create a new coffee</a>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
    <p>If you need any help, please don't hesitate to contact me!</p>
    <p>- Baristretto team </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>

